content: How do you see the detailed results for the autograder for PSETs/ microquizzes? I am getting significantly worse scores on the actual autograder than I am for the PSET tester or microquiz autograder while I am taking it, and want to see where I am actually going wrong.
subject: pset/microquiz scores

content: We do not reveal autograder results directly to students. I would recommend going to OH and asking a TA for help on how you could improve your code
